threads.title: 820-00165 - no known liquid, does not start
threads.message:
Check voltage at all big coils.
See if them pulse at least and which ones do that.
ALL_SYS_PWRGD pulsing too?
This symptom could be sign of corrupted BIOS.
Try new one, with clean ME.
